The 4Geeks Academy offers a Course in Applied Artificial Intelligence designed for professionals looking to integrate AI into various industries and roles. This six-week program includes 2 live online classes each week with a maximum class size of 12 students. No prior knowledge of AI is required, making it accessible to all. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Participants will learn about generative AI, prompts, models, and best practices to enhance their workplace productivity. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop